reviewText: This is a great DVD for any preschool-aged Nickelodeon fan as it features all the best shows!  No commercials or missed shows, there is an episode for all six popular Nickelodeon characters.  While these episodes have previously aired on Nickelodeon my boys loved having them all on one DVD that they could watch anytime and anywhere.  It is a music and danced filled DVD with the episodes all focusing on fun!
Title: Nickelodeon Favorites: Dance to the Music

reviewText: If your kids love nick shows than this is a great video. Get your kids moving with Dora and the bubble guppies.
Title: Nickelodeon Favorites: Dance to the Music

reviewText: My 4 year old daughter loves to dance and loves all of the nick jr characters who are in this dvd.  The quality is great and she loves it!!
summary: Great dvd to get your little ones movin!!
Title: Nickelodeon Favorites: Dance to the Music

reviewText: Both my 5 yr. old and 2 yr. old grand-daughters liked this, but just didn't really love it. They watched it once and haven't asked to watch it again. I say it's good- just not great.
Title: Nickelodeon Favorites: Dance to the Music

reviewText: Again I bought this for my granddaughter  and she enjoys all of the Dora movies she has  so if you have a little girl I would recommend this movie
